                    "body": "There are some classes which could be detached:\n\nZend_Feed_Builder_Header_Itunes (line 115)\nZend_Feed_Builder_Header (lines 178, 249, 272)\nZend_InfoCard (line 144)",
                    "updateAuthor": {
